{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-describe-places-and-events/task-40","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-describe-places-and-events","challengeType":19,"description":"","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Da biste saznali koliko ljudi obično učestvuje na hakatonu, pronađite deo teksta koji govori o učešću. Obratite pažnju na rečenicu koja prethodi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Usually, around...</span> da biste dobili tačan broj.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"English","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Pročitajte tekst i odgovorite na pitanje koje se nalazi ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-describe-places-and-events/task-40"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Ovo je sažetak razgovora Lise i Boba:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Lisa is excited about the next hackathon. She plans to develop a new app for real-time project collaboration.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Her team includes a couple of developers from the Seattle branch and a UX designer she has worked with before. They are thinking of calling the app \"CollabReal.\"</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Usually, around fifty people join these events. Bob is interested and asks where he can find more information.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Lisa offers to help him sign up and asks when he is free to go over the form. Bob suggests meeting tomorrow during lunch, and Lisa agrees.</span></p>\n<p>Koliko ljudi obično učestvuje na hakatonu?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Pedeset ljudi.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Dvadeset ljudi.</p>","feedback":"<p>Pisani radovi ne zahtevaju dvadeset ljudi.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Dva programera.</p>","feedback":"<p>Mnogi ljudi učestv